node.text:
As an 18 year old if you told me I’d write a book one day I would’ve laughed at you. Where I come from, not many books are written about the lives we’ve lived. We are so focused on just making it to the next day. 

But today, the hard copies arrived and it’s a proud moment. I made it. 

Pre-order with the link in my bio.

#WhereTomorrowsArentPromised
